          "ins_item_num": null,
          "ins_total": null,
          "f9": "The insurance report left out the Step Flashing.\n\nWe are adding 68 LF of step flashing.\n\n1. During the roof tear-off process, the existing step flashing is disturbed and cannot be reused. New step flashing must be installed to maintain a proper weather-tight seal between the roof deck and the adjacent wall.\n   a. Please see attached EagleView Report for confirmation of the measurements.",
